19 November 2007

This is v0.1.0 of YoutubeService module.

You can find the documentation at : http://doc.silverstripe.com/doku.php?id=modules:youtubeservice

To install :

1. Place this directory in the root of your SilverStripe installation
I.e. you will now have the following root folders

assets
mysite
cms
jsparty
sapphire
gallery

2. Run /db/build/


3. The CMS should now have a new "YoutubeGallery" page type.
   Create a page and set the parameters correctly on 'Videos' tab to grab the videos for display.

4. If you have blog module installed, this you could use the YoutubeWidget which comes with this module.

5. Add these and visit your public site to reflect the changes

:: NOTE ::
If you are still using deprecated all-in-one mashups module, please remove it before installing this. All other functionalities which were available in mashups module are now available in separate modules.

Please raise issues, bugs, contributions in the silverstripe.com forum...

lakshan@silverstripe.com

